WITH _ AS (
                    UPDATE debounce_key
                    SET debounced_times = 0,
                        first_started_at = now(),
                        previous_job_id = NULL
                    WHERE job_id = $1
                )
                UPDATE v2_job_debounce_batch
                SET debounce_batch = nextval('debounce_batch_seq')
                WHERE id = $1
